<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q30_v6" title="Q30_v6" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      En un museo de arte hay un panel informativo que muestra la fórmula de Euler para ciertos poliedros:
      <m:math>
        <m:mi>C</m:mi>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo>
        <m:mi>V</m:mi>
        <m:mo>=</m:mo>
        <m:mi>A</m:mi>
        <m:mo>+</m:mo>
        <m:mn>2</m:mn>
      </m:math>, donde C es la cantidad de caras, V es la cantidad de vértices y A es la cantidad de aristas del poliedro.
    </p>
    <p>
      Debajo del panel se describe una escultura poliedral en una lista: «Esta escultura tiene 12 caras y 18 aristas y cumple la fórmula de Euler mostrada arriba».
      ¿Cuántos vértices tiene esa escultura?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">6<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math>. Pero <m:math><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>, esa opción no cumple la fórmula.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">8<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Al reemplazar <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math> en <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>, se obtiene <m:math><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">20<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:math>. Pero <m:math><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>, esa opción no cumple la fórmula.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">32<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn></m:math>, entonces <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>32</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>44</m:mn></m:math>. Pero <m:math><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mn>44</m:mn><m:mo>≠</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>, esa opción no cumple la fórmula.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Escribir la fórmula de Euler</strong></p>
            <p>La fórmula entregada es <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reemplazar los datos del problema</strong></p>
            <p>La escultura tiene 12 caras y 18 aristas, por lo tanto <m:math><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:math> y <m:math><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Al sustituir, queda <m:math><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Simplificar el lado derecho</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>, así que la ecuación queda <m:math><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Despejar la cantidad de vértices</strong></p>
            <p>Restamos 12 en ambos lados: <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>20</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Entonces <m:math><m:mi>V</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>8</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La escultura tiene <strong>8 vértices</strong>. La alternativa correcta es <strong>ChoiceB</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>